schools.name: Fountain Lake Middle School Cobra Digital Prep Academy

data.description: Perfect location on East end of the Village, 2.5 miles to the Balboa Gate and in the coveted Fountain Lake School District!  Level, zero maintenance yard complements  the beautiful setting of our 3/2 with sunroom.  A woodburning fireplace provides a focal point for the large great room/dining room combo which is just steps from the large deck with retractable awning, perfect for all your entertaining plans.  The spacious kitchen with an abundance of oak cabinets and solid surface countertops will be a pleasure for the cook in your family.  Beautiful wood clad windows brighten up the entire home letting natural sunshine illuminate every corner.  Built in cabinets in the laundry room provide that much needed storage.  New heat pump, water heater, roof, appliances, and interior and exterior painting all completed within the last 4 years.  A $1500 buy in will be charged to new HSV buyers.
